title: Zeits of the Round Table 1/27: Kobe, Chris Wallace, Google Docs, Tyler the Creator
itunes:title: Zeits of the Round Table 1/27: Kobe, Chris Wallace, Google Docs, Tyler the Creator
description:
On this edition of Zeits of the Round Table Jack and Miles discuss the tragic passing of Kobe and Gianna Bryant as well as 7 other passengers in a helicopter crash, Chris Wallace putting the heat on the Senate, Google docs went down, and Tyler the Creator rightfully calls out the racism of the Grammys.
